#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.compress.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.compress"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:1 of
msgid "Return selected slices of a tensor along given axis."
msgstr "返回沿给定轴的张量的选定切片。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:3 of
msgid ""
"When working along a given axis, a slice along that axis is returned in "
"`output` for each index where `condition` evaluates to True. When working"
" on a 1-D array, `compress` is equivalent to `extract`."
msgstr ""
"当沿着给定轴工作时，对于 `condition` 为 True 的每个索引，将返回沿该轴的"
"一个切片到 `output` 中。当处理一维数组时，`compress` 等价于 `extract`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:7 of
msgid ""
"Tensor that selects which entries to return. If len(condition) is less "
"than the size of `a` along the given axis, then output is truncated to "
"the length of the condition tensor."
msgstr ""
"选择要返回哪些条目的张量。如果 `condition` 的长度小于 `a` 沿给定轴的大小"
"，则输出会被截断为条件张量的长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:11 of
msgid "Tensor from which to extract a part."
msgstr "要从中提取部分的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:13 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which to take slices. If None (default), work on the flattened"
" tensor."
msgstr "沿其取切片的轴。如果为 None（默认值），则在展平后的张量上操作。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:16 of
msgid ""
"Output tensor.  Its type is preserved and it must be of the right shape "
"to hold the output."
msgstr "输出张量。其类型会被保留，并且必须具有能够容纳输出结果的正确形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:20 of
msgid ""
"**compressed_array** -- A copy of `a` without the slices along axis for "
"which `condition` is false."
msgstr ""
"**compressed_array** -- 一个 `a` 的副本，其中移除了 `condition` 为假值的"
"轴上的切片。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:26 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`take`, :py:obj:`choose`, :py:obj:`diag`, :py:obj:`diagonal`, "
":py:obj:`select`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.compress`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:29 of
msgid "Equivalent method in ndarray"
msgstr "ndarray 中的等效方法"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.extract`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:32 of
msgid "Equivalent method when working on 1-D arrays"
msgstr "处理一维数组时的等效方法"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:35 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.compress.compress:53 of
msgid ""
"Working on the flattened tensor does not return slices along an axis but "
"selects elements."
msgstr "对展平张量进行操作不会返回沿轴的切片，而是选择元素。"

